    "title": "Pronoun Case",
    "body": "Choose pronoun case by the pronoun's job. Subjects take I, he, she, they, who; objects take me, him, her, them, whom. In compounds, test the pronoun alone to hear the right case.",
    "key_points": [
      "Subjective case for subjects (I, who).",
      "Objective case for objects (me, whom).",
      "In compounds, drop the other name to check."
    ]
